error.message: Class Drupal\Tests\dynamic_date\FunctionalJavascript\DynamicDateIntegrationTest extends deprecated class Drupal\FunctionalJavascriptTests\JavascriptTestBase. Deprecated in drupal:8.6.0 and is removed from drupal:9.0.0. Use \Drupal\FunctionalJavascriptTests\WebDriverTestBase instead
